},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:34:33.000Z","msg":"唔知 所以咪要問下囉"},{"pid":"2790c4f845e4d0269655bf13ab93fdaff3b0c672","tid":1739804,"uid":52092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:35:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7ea1d9856f2273e45cddfe512c5c4c88ecd8bff","tid":1739804,"uid":36807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:35:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可以投票</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgjzS07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgjzS07.jpg&h=7fd385a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFake news:《小心俾人拘留 導致無法投票》<br />\n❗️其實理論上係唔會因為拘留而冇得投票❗️<br />\n要認清楚 同捍衛自己權利 <br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;&rsquo;遭懲教署囚禁或羈押的選民可在設於有關懲教署院 所的專用投票站投票。&lsquo;&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;&rsquo;而警署內亦會設立專用投票站，以供被其他執法機構羈押或拘留的選民投票。&lsquo;&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n囚禁：囚犯已定罪 服刑中<br />\n羈押：未定罪 不可保釋 待審訊<br />\n拘留：扣押48小時 <br />\n<br />\n以上三種都可以投票<br />\n<br />\n當然俾狗玩狗野嘅話 就冇辦法 要記低佢編號 時間等等 可要求聯絡律師 等律師做證及協助<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/pdf/2019DCE_Candidates_Briefing_Chairman_Speech_(Sup_Info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fdc2019%2Fpdf%2F2019DCE_Candidates_Briefing_Chairman_Speech_%28Sup_Info&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=d4a088e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/pdf/2019DCE_Candidates_Briefing_Chairman_Speech_(Sup_Info</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\n如果有專業人士睇到有誤 求指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ae21d0e8978977ac3e0de792447515dffa2177","tid":1739804,"uid":52092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7ea1d9856f2273e45cddfe512c5c4c88ecd8bff","tid":1739804,"uid":36807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"ci