2:49:11.000Z","msg":"佢比你投先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f6aafe21001a6d9dca464f0546638df4f82fd4","tid":1739804,"uid":224255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:51:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32c704eb34cdfa1dec3cc342acba6e81653f58f5","tid":1739804,"uid":111669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:05:56.000Z","msg":"有得投架！<br />\n<br />\n根據《選舉（舞弊及非法行為）條例》第14（1）（e）或（f）條 ，妨礙或阻止他人在選舉中投票；讓另一人阻礙或阻止第三人在選舉中投票，一經定罪，最高可判處罰款50萬元及監禁7年。"}]}